{"tid":2447829,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東海航空機長及乘務長航程期間互毆　決定對涉事兩人予終身停飛","createTime":"2021-03-15T12:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T13:08:59.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4eefed7f3caab4e5344fe2762c576506f9d59865","tid":2447829,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"東海航空一班由南通飛往西安的航班，上月飛行期間，機組人員互毆，東航通過官方微信公眾號發布，對涉事機長及乘務長，給予公司終身停飛處理。<br />\n<br />\n相關決定表示，東航2&middot;20事件造成極其惡劣社會影響，涉事兩人嚴重違反民航法規、行業規章及公司規章制度。東航對4名公司領導和11名中層管理人員，給予免職、在公司內部進行通報批評等不同程度處罰。<br />\n<br />\n有網友反映，東航DZ6297南通至西安航班上，機長與乘務長發生爭執，在飛行過程中相互毆打，導致雙方受傷。東海正全面開展安全整頓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580733-20210315.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580733-20210315.htm&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDqwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=36e065b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580733-20210315.htm&h=e5144f21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580733-20210315.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5d0d618121797e400994e59a63f0a139a5e43191","tid":2447829,"uid":247211,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:54:01.000Z","msg":"乘務長賺左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488c5e7dc70e452f2dea83f6fa82c0b741b5bca3","tid":2447829,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:54:16.000Z","msg":"食左空姐?"},{"pid":"7ef66a761a8d4e164c8250a9b630837ddc61f67a","tid":2447829,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2fe9271cdfa4e59597710ff57b6e03b0207000","tid":2447829,"uid":194281,"like":